entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have discovered that the Chirq Council is lead by the nine members of the Elite Council.
entries.journal_entry_description: Infiltrate the Chirq Council by earning the trust of one of the underbosses. Use that trust to find the leaders of the Chirq Council.
entries.journal_entry_title: The Chirq Council: Moving Up - Part Two
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Take the fake CorSec ID to Jzoro and convince him that Ebela was an undercover CorSec agent posing as a terrorist.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Take the Fake CorSec ID to Jzoro
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Jzoro was impressed with the way you handled the undercover CorSec agent. He now trusts you and has provided you with access to his mainframe. Use the mainframe to learn who controls the Chirq Council. Don't worry about blowing your cover. Take out anyone who gets in your way.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: Learn who Leads of the Chirq Council
entries.task02_task_display_string_1: Find Out who Controls the Chirq Council
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Report to Captain Baize with news of your success.
entries.task04_item_name: You have downloaded the identities of the Chirq Council leaders
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Use Jzoro's mainframe. Download any information about the Chirq Council's leaders.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: You learn that the Chirq Council is controlled by nine people who are known as the Elite Council.
entries.task05_message_box_text: You learn that the Chirq Council is controlled by nine people who are known as the Elite Council.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Make sure there are no witnesses. Defeat some Chirq Council lookouts.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Make sure there are no witnesses. Defeat some Chirq Council wardens.
